creator: Swob Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Download. Swipe. Hired! Swob™, a FREE app, was designed to make job searching easy and convenient. Through the use of technology, you can now search for a job in the comfort of your own phone™. Swob is the first of its kind to target students in high turnover industries such as retail, and food services for part-time, seasonal and full-time employment.


Swob is the most convenient way to apply to a variety of available job positions. Finding the right job can be tough, and Swob lets you find your ideal position in the industry of your choice, with a simple swipe.


1. Download Swob.

2. Quickly and Easily create your profile and look for available jobs in the industry and location of your choice.

3. Swipe to find a job!
